# WW-Chat-AI Component Overview

This WeWeb element provides a customizable chat interface for web applications.

## Key Files

- [src/wwElement.vue](mdc:src/wwElement.vue) - The main component that orchestrates all functionality
- [ww-config.js](mdc:ww-config.js) - WeWeb element configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts

## Component Structure

The chat is built from several Vue components:
- [src/components/ChatHeader.vue](mdc:src/components/ChatHeader.vue) - The chat header with user info
- [src/components/MessageList.vue](mdc:src/components/MessageList.vue) - The message display area
- [src/components/InputArea.vue](mdc:src/components/InputArea.vue) - The input field and controls

## Utility Functions

- [src/utils/dateTimeFormatter.js](mdc:src/utils/dateTimeFormatter.js) - Functions for formatting dates and times
